   <conbody>
      <p>To start the Adapter cluster, execute the following command:</p>
      <codeblock>besr_cluster start adapters</codeblock>
      <p>To stop the Adapter cluster, execute the following command:</p>
      <codeblock>besr_cluster stop adapters</codeblock>
      <p>To check whether the Adapter cluster is running, execute the following command:</p>
      <codeblock>besr_cluster status adapters</codeblock>
   </conbody>
</concept>